------------
v3.0.0alpha6
------------

[rla] Controller Framework Routes now work correctly for separate subdomain or
      for uncommon webdir layouts.
[rla] Controller Framework now has limited capabilities for unauthenticated or
      API-authenticated calls.
[rla] Adapt schema migrations to work in new H6 installation layout.
[rla] Added injectable wrapper around Config to reduce globals access.
[rla] With Marco Abbrancati: Upgraded test cases for phpunit 9.x utility.


